frames.caption: A joyful scene unfolds as a large, fluffy cat and a young girl ride on dolphins through vibrant ocean waves. The girl, wearing a swimsuit with a cat design, stretches her arms wide in excitement, while the cat appears equally thrilled. Seagulls soar above, adding to the lively atmosphere of the ocean adventure.
frames.description: The scene depicts a whimsical and fantastical setting where a cat and a girl are riding dolphins in the ocean. The bright and colorful environment suggests a playful and adventurous mood.
